# Proxmox VE System Limits
# Optimized for containers, VMs, and monitoring tools

# Max open files (containers, monitoring, Docker)
* soft nofile 1048576
* hard nofile 1048576
root soft nofile 1048576
root hard nofile 1048576

# Max processes (LXC, nested containers)
* soft nproc 65535
* hard nproc 65535
root soft nproc 65535
root hard nproc 65535

# Locked memory (GPU passthrough, DPDK, VFIO)
* soft memlock unlimited
* hard memlock unlimited
root soft memlock unlimited
root hard memlock unlimited

